About

As an Oakland-native born during the tech boom in Silicon Valley, Vanessa has always been interested in technology and has been working on computers for as long as she can remember. She learned that through code, she could create whatever she dreamt of. Even more, she loves how self-reliant coding makes you. Whether your code works or not, is up to you. Vanessa, seeing the similarities between coding and art, decided to pursue and master both.


Vanessa is a Full-stack Web Developer and Artist. Her speciality is JavaScript, which is the language that predominantly controls the internet. She also freelances and offers speaking engagements and mentorship. Her career has been diverse, from working with e-commerce start-ups to major international coding companies.


If you would like to work with Vanessa, contact her using the contact form on the Contact page.

); }; export default About;
